                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360201-528-offence-1 t18360201-cd-107"></join>8th of January</rs>, 15 pennies, and 30 halfpence, the monies of <persName id="t18360201-name-849" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-849" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
